{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287534, "create_time": 1657505946, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "用户习惯", "timestamp": 1657505946}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287535, "create_time": 1657505952, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "比如居然不能自定义切换输入法的快捷键，只能选，导致有些游戏直接没法玩了。也没有自带的工作区。\n\n丑得不行这个就不多说了。", "timestamp": 1657505952}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287581, "create_time": 1657507899, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "软件支持很大程度上决定了用户规模；\n目前用linux难免会遇到奇奇怪怪的小问题，比如连接校园网，KDE桌面没法连tsinghua-secure，尚未找到解决方案；\n显卡驱动大概也还是问题", "timestamp": 1657507899}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 288088, "create_time": 1657524549, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "软件支持性生态就是最重要的问题了，其他其实都不是问题。你找不到可以用的相关软件或者相关软件虽然支持linux但是实际表现问题百出的时候就会很痛苦了。另外各种驱动配起来相当费劲，包括但不限于显卡声卡", "timestamp": 1657524549}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 288240, "create_time": 1657530018, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "软件支持程度很难说是纯外部因素", "timestamp": 1657530018}], "create_time": 1657505696, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1657530018, "likenum": 7, "n_attentions": 7, "n_comments": 5, "pid": 81330, "poll": null, "reply": 5, "text": "问一个问题，除了软件支持程度这种纯外部因素，现在Windows相比Linux还有什么优势吗？\n感觉不仅稳定性、性能、磁盘占用大小，现在连桌面环境的美观程度和用户友好程度都被Linux常用的gnome/unity/kde等桌面环境吊起来打了", "timestamp": 1657505696}}